cs.SI, cs.SOC, cs.CYBER, cs.DL, cs.HC 

The paper discusses the dynamics of online social networks, which falls under the scope of social computing (cs.SI) and social networks (cs.SOC). The use of epidemiological models to explain user adoption and abandonment of OSNs also relates to cybersecurity (cs.CYBER) and machine learning (cs.DL) as the authors use data to validate their model. Additionally, the paper discusses the implications of OSN dynamics on user behavior and mental health, which falls under the scope of human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
